-- Tata Motors to Offer Four-Year Warranty, Maintenance Contract for Nano Car
-- B y   V i p i n   N a i r
-- 2010-12-09T06:57:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-09/tata-motors-to-offer-four-year-warranty-maintenance-contract-for-nano-car.html
Tata Motors Ltd. today said it will
offer a four year warranty for its Nano car as the automaker
seeks to boost sales of the hatchback.  New buyers of the car will also have the option to get a
maintenance contract at 99 rupees a month, according to a
company statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vipin Nair at 
 vnair12@bloomberg.net  